headline: Robinhood, Schwab Stocks Hit Hard in Market Tumble
summary: Brokerage stocks are among the hardest-hit in today’s selloff. Robinhood stock sank more than 10% in Monday morning trading, while shares of Interactive Brokers tumbled 8%. Charles Schwab stock fell 4.
